# Environment Variables Template
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values for local development
# For production (Render/Railway), set these in the platform's dashboard

# MongoDB Connection (REQUIRED)
# For MongoDB Atlas: mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/?retryWrites=true&w=majority
